globally oriented media service shall adopt following code ethics pursuance vision mission set 1. adhere journalistic values honesty courage fairness balance independence credibility diversity giving priority commercial political professional consideration 2. endeavour get truth declare dispatches programmes news bulletins unequivocally manner leaves doubt validity accuracy 3. treat audiences due respect address every issue story due attention present clear factual accurate picture giving full consideration feelings victims crime war persecution disaster relatives viewers individual privacies public decorum 4. welcome fair honest media competition without allowing affect adversely standards performance thereby “ scoop ” would become end 5. present diverse points view opinions without bias partiality 6. recognise diversity human societies races cultures beliefs values intrinsic individualities present unbiased faithful reflection 7. acknowledge mistake occurs promptly correct ensure recur 8. observe transparency dealing news sources adhering internationally established practices concerning rights sources 9. distinguish news material opinion analysis avoid snares speculation propaganda 10. stand colleagues profession give support required particularly light acts aggression harassment journalists subjected times cooperate arab international journalistic unions associations defend freedom press source media journalism
